=== Droxidopa

Norepinephrine prodrug that crosses the BBB. Probes central norepinephrine deficiency (documented CSF catecholamine reduction @Walitt2024NIH). ==== If droxidopa works

central norepinephrine deficiency was functionally significant — one of few medications directly probing the CSF catecholamine finding.

*Certainty*   Low to Medium — no ME/CFS RCT.

*Level of action*   Partial root cause.